data.description: Welcome home to this absolutely charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom, two-car garage home set on a spacious acre of land, offering breathtaking mountain views! Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this beautifully maintained property provides the perfect blend of comfort, privacy, and convenience. Step through the front door and into the cozy living room, where you'll immediately be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room flows seamlessly into the dining area, making it the perfect space for hosting family gatherings and intimate dinners. You'll love indulging your culinary creativity in the well-equipped kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and a pantry to keep everything organized. Through the kitchen's door, you'll find a patio and large fenced-in backyard with a firepit for entertaining. Rounding out the main level is a convenient bedroom that could double as a spacious office space. Also don't miss the full bathroom! Venturing upstairs, you'll discover two additional bedrooms one offering a walk-in closet with each offering ample space and comfort. A full bathroom completes the upper level. The home's thoughtful design also includes a two-car garage and storage shed, providing ample storage for your vehicles and belongings. Plus, its convenient location just minutes from grocery stores, shopping, and Interstate 25, insures easy access to everyday necessities and nearby attractions.
